data.actual_result: The dark overlay from the upload popup is below the server menu and the previous context menu.
data.expected_result: The dark overlay from the upload popup should be on top of everything and the previous context menu should close
data.short_description: The upload popup has a lower z-index than the server menu and previous context menu does not close.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to any guild - Open the server menu by clicking on the server name (right-clicking anywhere also has the same effect) - Without clicking on discord, either drag a file into discord or paste an image from the clipboard into the message box
